				 Road rage with iron rod
																								New Delhi, Oct. 3 (PTI): A minibus driver allegedly hit a doctors wife with an iron rod after an altercation over rash driving.																								The incident took place in Mayur Vihar of East Delhi around 8am when the doctor, Abid, and his wife Roshan were on their way in their car to drop their daughter to school.																								Coming from the wrong side, the minibus almost hit the car, following which the woman asked the driver to be careful. The enraged driver, Vicky, took out an iron rod and hit the woman on her head. She has a cut above her eye, the doctor said.																								The driver was arrested.
